arcgis_maps.description: ArcGIS Maps SDK for Flutter is a plugin for ArcGIS Maps SDK for Kotlin and ArcGIS Maps SDK for Swift (Not available) created by Ludycom S.A.S. Currently in beta, it is planned to be used in production, the plugin will allow users to use ArcGIS maps through a customizable and optimized widget.
